Package: intCPUEextra
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Area CPUE Standardization Based on intCPUE
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-03-02
Authors@R: 
    person("Rujia", "Bi", , "rbi@iattc.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1954-6797"))
Description: Extends intCPUE to joint multi-area catch-per-unit-effort (CPUE)
    standardization using Template Model Builder (TMB). Vessel effects,
    fishery-level mean differences, and flag-specific temporal deviations are
    shared across areas. Temporal and latent population components remain
    area-specific, while flag-specific spatial deviations use a dedicated
    full-domain mesh with their own anisotropy and covariance parameters.
